`HTML Injection`

HTML Injection can occur on input fields where there is no input validation and output encoded. 

If you find any iput filed first try checking if any special characters can be included. If yes, try HTML code in the input field. 
Set the bwapp as low level 
Next try mentionig the Hello in first name and include the HTML code in last name as <b>Hi</b>
You should be able to see welcome `Hello hi` HI in the last name will appear in BOLD format. 

